 believe that BIR@ECIR is a much needed scientific event for the =
=E2=80=98retrievalists=E2=80=99 and =E2=80=98citationists=E2=80=99 to =
meet and join forces pushing the knowledge boundaries of IR applied to =
literature search and recommendation.<o:p class=3D""></o:p></p><p =
