Submission Details =3D=3D=3D<o:p class=3D""></o:p></p><p =
class=3D"MsoPlainText">All submissions must be written in English =
following Springer LNCS author guidelines (6 to 12 pages, pleae see =
below) and should be submitted as PDF files to EasyChair. All =
submissions will be reviewed by at least two independent reviewers.
 Please be aware of the fact that at least one author per paper needs to =
register for the workshop and attend the workshop to present the work. =
In case of no-show the paper (even if accepted) will be deleted from the =
proceedings AND from the program.<o:p class=3D""></o:p></p><p =
